"title": "1185: God, zeal of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1185: god, zeal of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The intense and protective commitment of God to his people and to his purposes which seeks a passionate and obedient response. The zeal of God is often linked with the idea of the “jealousy of God”, in which God refuses to contemplate his people giving their allegiance or affection to another.</p>\n<h2>God in his zeal demands exclusive loyalty from his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5\">EXO 20:5</a></strong> <em>The jealousy of God implies that he seeks for and insists on exclusive loyalty which is due to him and which will benefit those who give it.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:14\">EXO 34:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:24\">DEU 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:9\">DEU 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:19\">JOS 24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2\">NAM 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's zeal for the honour of his name</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:8\">ISA 42:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:7\">EXO 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:51\">DEU 32:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:9-Isa48:11\">ISA 48:9–48:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:9\">EZK 20:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:14\">EZK 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:22\">EZK 20:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:20-Ezek36:23\">EZK 36:20–36:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:7\">EZK 39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:25\">EZK 39:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's zeal on behalf of his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:14\">ZEC 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:31\">2KI 19:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:32\">ISA 37:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:18\">JOL 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:2\">ZEC 8:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's zeal to establish the Messiah's reign</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's zeal is aroused by his people's idolatry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:16\">DEU 32:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:20\">DEU 29:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:21\">DEU 32:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:22\">1KI 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:58\">PSA 78:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:3\">EZK 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:5\">EZK 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:38\">EZK 16:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:25\">EZK 23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:21-1Cor10:22\">1CO 10:21–10:22</a></p>\n<h2>God's zeal in judgment</h2>\n<h3>He judges the nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:5-Ezek36:6\">EZK 36:5–36:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:18-Ezek38:19\">EZK 38:18–38:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>He restrains his zeal in judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:42\">EZK 16:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:11\">NUM 25:11</a></p>\n<h3>God's people appeal for his zeal to be shown</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:15\">ISA 63:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:10-Ps74:11\">PSA 74:10–74:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:11\">ISA 26:11</a></p>\n<h2>God's people reflect his zeal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:11-Num25:13\">NUM 25:11–25:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:17\">PRO 23:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:11\">ROM 12:11</a></p>",
